USAGE:

1. Install this bundle
2. Hit CMD + S
3. Behold as trailing whitespace disappears into the infernal maw of Galzroth, Devourer of Whitespace
4. Make everyone you work with install this bundle
5. Enjoy your new life, free of whitespace diffs

FAQ:

Q: Why is this bundle called "Galzroth, Devourer of Whitespace"?
A: Because Stone Cold said so.